{"word":"Βοανηργές","slug":"Βοανηργές","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Βοανηργές</el></b> [derivation uncertain; the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transl.\">transl.</a> <el>υἱοὶ βροντῆς</el> may reflect folk etymology] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ indecl.\">indecl.</a> <b><i>Boanerges,</i></b> surname, in effect a nickname, given by Jesus to the sons of Zebedee <b><a href='B:480 3:17'>Mk 3:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βλητέος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:βοάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}